other non-descendants.

00:09:05.895 --> 00:09:07.320
All right?

00:09:07.320 --> 00:09:10.590
Now I can start scratching
stuff out.

00:09:10.590 --> 00:09:11.690
Well, let's see.

00:09:11.690 --> 00:09:16.120
I know that C, from my diagram,
has only one parent,

00:09:16.120 --> 00:09:21.080
D. So given its parent, it's
independent of all other

00:09:21.080 --> 00:09:22.730
