00:09:37.190 --> 00:09:41.460
B is conditional on T and R.
Ah, but B has no parent.

00:09:41.460 --> 00:09:45.120
So it actually is independent
of those two guys.

00:09:45.120 --> 00:09:48.330
The trashcan, yeah, that's
dependent on R. And R over

00:09:48.330 --> 00:09:50.640
here, the final thing in the
chain, that's just a

00:09:50.640 --> 00:09:53.160
