00:23:43.540 --> 00:23:45.240
the probability of B--

00:23:45.240 --> 00:23:46.680
I'm just multiplying it out--

00:23:46.680 --> 00:23:48.050
it equal to that joint
probability.

00:23:52.690 --> 00:23:57.715
Oh, but by symmetry, there's no
